reviewText: This is a soft core Japanese BDSM movie, with four cute girls of various body types, tying each up in various ways and doing some mild whipping and such.  Amazingly enough it's uncensored, not that there's any "pink".  There are several very hot scenes, all just the girls in various combinations, ruined only by a couple absurd squirting shots.  But given the general wall to wall flawless Japanese girl flesh on display here, just about any silliness is excusable, including the inclusion of a Christian cult.  With bondage.  I have no idea, and who cares, check it out.
